>ショップページ</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/business/service.html\">ビジネス</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recruit\">採用情報</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/contact.html\">お問い合わせ</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"spNavigationTrigger\" class=\" c-sp_navigation_btn\"></div>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</header>\n</div>\n<div id=\"a-billboard\" class=\"a-billboard    cssskin-_area_billboard\">\n<div class=\"site_frame\">\n<section>\n<div id=\"bk15766300\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal bd-sm-smart cssskin-business-hero02 init-block_animation\" data-bk-id=\"bk15766300\" data-animated=\"fadeIn\">\n<div class=\" column -column1\">\n<h2 class=\" c-title c-center\"><span class=\" webfont1\">COMPANY</span></h2>\n<h3 class=\" c-large_headline c-center\">企業情報</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main>\n<div id=\"a-site_contents\" class=\"a-site_contents  noskin\">\n<article>\n<div class=\"site_frame\">\n<div class=\"g-column\">\n<div id=\"a-main\" class=\"a-main column -col12 \">\n<section>\n<div id=\"bk15969372\" class=\"b-album c-sp-space_narrow bd-sm-smart cssskin-business-nav-new\" data-bk-id=\"bk15969372\">\n<div class=\" g-column -col6 -sp-col2 -no_spacing\">\n<div class=\" column -column1\">\n<div class=\" c-body c-center\">\n PROFILE\n<br>会社概要\n<br>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\" column -column2\">\n<div class=\" c-body c-center\">\n<a href=\"company_philosophy.html\" data-pid=\"1245084\">PHILOSOPHY<br>企業理念・行動指針</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\" column -column3\">\n<div class=\" c-body c-center\">\n<a href=\"health.html\" data-pid=\"1257982\">HEALTH<br>健康経営宣言</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\" column -column4\">\n<div class=\" c-body c-center\">\n<a href=\"company_history.html\" data-pid=\"1245085\">HISTORY<br>沿革</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\" column -column5\">\n<div class=\" c-body c-center\">\n<a href=\"company_chart.html\" data-pid=\"1245086\">CHART<br>組織図</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\" column -column6 -column-lasts\">\n<div class=\" c-body c-center\">\n<a href=\"company_office.html\" data-pid=\"1245089\">OFFICE<br>事務所一覧</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"bk15766295\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_init cssskin-sub-company\" data-bk-id=\"bk15766295\">\n<div class=\" g-column -col2 -sp-col1\">\n<div class=\" column -column1\">\n<h2 class=\" c-title c-center\"><span class=\" webfont1\">PROFILE</span></h2>\n<h3 class=\" c-large_headline c-center\">会社概要</h3>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">会社名</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">アイ・ティー・エックス株式会社<br>（ITX株式会社）</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">設立年月日</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">2014年12月1日</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">営業開始年月日</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">2000年4月1日</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">資本金</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">2億円</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">従業員数</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">2,376名（2025年4月1日現在）</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">株主構成</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">株式会社ノジマ 100％</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n</div>\n<div class=\" column -column2 -column-lasts\">\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">代表取締役社長</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">野尻　幸宏</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">取締役会長</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">石坂　洋三</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">取締役相談役</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">野島　廣司</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">取締役兼執行役員　</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">眞境名　奈保</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">取締役</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">日坂　聡</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">監査役</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">國實　耕平</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">執行役員</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">滝　晃一<br>神田　典弘<br>藤原　司</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">事業内容</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">テレコム事業を中心とした情報通信サービス事業</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">主要取引先</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">株式会社NTTドコモ<br>東日本電信電話株式会社（NTT東日本）<br>西日本電信電話株式会社（NTT西日本）<br>NTTドコモビジネス株式会社<br>ソフトバンク株式会社</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n<p class=\"c-lead\">古物商許可証番号　　　　　</p>\n<p class=\"c-note\">神奈川県公安委員会<br>第451930007690号（平成27年6月19日）<br>アイ・ティー・エックス株式会社</p>\n<p class=\" c-body\"><br class=\"clear\"></p>\n<hr class=\"c-hr\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n</main>\n<div id=\"a-footer\" data-float=\"false\" class=\"a-footer   cssskin-_area_footer\">\n<footer>\n<div class=\"site_frame\">\n<div id=\"bk15766298\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_footer\" data-bk-id=\"bk15766298\" data-shared=\"true\" data-sharedname=\"footer\">\n<div class=\" column -column1\">\n<h2 class=\" c-title c-center\"><span class=\" d-smallest_font\">アイ・ティー・エックス株式会社は株式会社ノジマのグループ会社です。</span></h2>\n<nav>\n<div class=\" -menu_center\">\n<ul class=\"c-menu -menu_b menu-parts\">\n<li><a href=\"/privacy.html\">プライバシーポリシー</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/security.html\">情報セキュリティ基本方針</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</nav>\n<div class=\"c-credit c-center\">\n<span>© 2021 ITX Corporation.</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</footer>\n</div>\n<div id=\"w-top-left\" class=\"w-base w-top w-left\">\n</div>\n<div id=\"w-top-right\" class=\"w-base w-top w-right\">\n</div>\n<div id=\"w-middle-left\" class=\"w-base w-middle w-left\">\n</div>\n<div id=\"w-middle-right\" class=\"w-base w-middle w-right\">\n</div>\n<div id=\"w-bottom-left\" class=\"w-base w-bottom w-left\">\n</div>\n<div id=\"w-bottom-right\" class=\"w-base w-bottom w-right\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n<!--\nvar css_list = ['//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:100,100italic,300,300italic,regular,italic,700,700italic,900,900italic&display=swap','//module.bindsite.jp/type-fonts/css/sourcehansans.css','//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Oswald:200,300,regular,500,600,700&display=swap','_csslinkbtn/btn-import.css'];\nvar page_update = 1779091571573;\n//-->\n</script>\n<script src=\"_module/lib/lib.js?v=15.0.8\" defer></script>\n<script src=\"_module/scripts/bind.js?v=15.0.8\" id=\"script-js\" defer></script>\n<!--[if lt IE 9]><script src=\"_module/lib/html5shiv.min.js?v=15.0.8\"></script><![endif]-->\n</body>\n</html>","finalUrl":"https://www.itx-corp.co.jp/company/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-14T19:30:04.187Z"}